<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/styles.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .image-text-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 20px auto;
            gap: 20px;
            max-width: 80%;
        }

        .image-text-container img {
            width: 50%;
            transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }

        .image-text-container img:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        }

        .image-text-container p {
            flex: 1;
            text-align: left;
        }

        p {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 10px auto;
            max-width: 80%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    
    <!--Navigation Bar-->
    <%- include('partials/navbar', { page: 'home' }) %>

    <!-- Explain Turtle Project -->
    <p>what is a turtle shelter vest? a high tech but simple solution to help save lives -
        a portable "shelter" you can carry with you, just like a turtle...</p>

    <div class="image-text-container">
        <p>One winter when Jen was homeless, 7 of her friends froze to death.  

        Jen is no longer homeless and has figured out a solution:
         High tech foam vests that are inexpensive,
        keep a person warm to 10 degree below zero, help SAVE lives and alleviate suffering.
        
        YOU can request vests for your community - and you can make vests and have your friends, business colleagues, church members or club make vests, too! </p>

        <img src="/redblueorangevests.png" alt="Friends in Vests">
    </div>

    <!-- Stats/Dashboard --> 

    <!-- Vests Distributed -->
    <p>Over 5,5000 vests have been made and distributed by volunteers like you. </p>

    <!-- Carousel Section -->
    <div id="vestCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <!-- Images from folder -->
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="/vest1.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Vest 1">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="/vest2.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Vest 2">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="/vest3.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Vest 3">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="/vest4.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Vest 4">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="/vest5.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Vest 5">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="/vest6.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Vest 6">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="/vest7.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Vest 7">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="/vest8.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Vest 8">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="/vest9.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Vest 9">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="/vest10.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Vest 10">
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Controls -->
        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#vestCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
        </button>
        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#vestCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
        </button>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
